          description: "",
          "content:encoded":
            '<p>"...Life is but a dream"</p>\n<p><span style="color:var(--color-text);">TranSCENTdence took our audiences on a magical and dreamy adventure through one girl\'s life. This concert expresses the girls\' sorrows and grievances, together with her source of strengths and newfound aspiration. </span></p>\n<p>An inspiring and relatable performance for audiences.</p>\n<p>To compliment our orchestra\'s performance, the following our graphics I designed</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone  wp-image-445" src="https://sciffany.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/version2_updated.png" alt="version2_updated" width="443" height="626" /></p>\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":451,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://sciffany.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/screenplay-5-e1549113053459.png?w=763" alt="" class="wp-image-451" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":455,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://sciffany.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/screenplay-e1549113202877.png?w=759" alt="" class="wp-image-455" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":454,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://sciffany.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/screenplay-8-e1549113173715.png?w=752" alt="" class="wp-image-454" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":453,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://sciffany.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/screenplay-7-e1549113151316.png?w=761" alt="" class="wp-image-453" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":449,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://sciffany.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/screenplay-3-e1549113021499.png?w=763" alt="" class="wp-image-449" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":452,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://sciffany.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/screenplay-6-e1549113128333.png?w=763" alt="" class="wp-image-452" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->',
